---
layout: base.njk
title: Le Signal
description: "Authored public signal from Forgotten Industries: recoveries, restorations, Le Rédempteur, doctrine, manifestos, field reports, and long-form entries suitable for the public feed."
permalink: /posts/index.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<section class="masthead">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">Public writing / RSS</p>
    <h1>Le Signal</h1>
    <p class="tagline">{{ description }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="evidence-band">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="signal-map">
      <p class="entry-note">
        <a href="/feed.xml">Subscribe to the public writing feed</a>. L'Archive
        remains the complete master record.
      </p>

      <div class="signal-branch-grid" aria-label="Le Signal branches">
        <a class="signal-branch-card signal-branch-card-active" href="#recoveries-restorations-le-redempteur">
          <span>Branch 01</span>
          <h2>Recoveries, Restorations, &amp; Le Rédempteur</h2>
          <p>The blog and main narrative: machines coming back, recovery-through-rebuild, memory, grief, craft, and evidence.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="signal-branch-card" href="#doctrine-manifestos">
          <span>Branch 02</span>
          <h2>Doctrine / Systems Manifestos</h2>
          <p>Principles, methods, operating language, archive theory, and the pieces that define how the work thinks.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="signal-branch-card" href="#field-reports">
          <span>Branch 03</span>
          <h2>Field Reports</h2>
          <p>Authored bench records and dated reports. More deliberate than live Bluesky, shorter than a full manuscript.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <section id="recoveries-restorations-le-redempteur" class="signal-section" aria-labelledby="signal-entries-heading">
        <p class="section-label">{{ collections.posts | count }} entries</p>
        <h2 id="signal-entries-heading">Manuscripts and public entries, newest first.</h2>
        <ol class="signal-entry-list" aria-label="All curated posts">
          {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
          <li>
            <header>
              <span>{% if post.data.entry %}Entry {{ post.data.entry }}{% else %}Entry{% endif %}</span>
              <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
            </header>
            <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
            <p class="entry-note">
              {% if post.data.type %}{{ post.data.type }}{% else %}Manuscript{% endif %}
              {% if post.data.category %}/ {{ post.data.category }}{% endif %}
            </p>
            {% if post.data.description %}
            <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            {% endif %}
          </li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section id="doctrine-manifestos" class="signal-section" aria-labelledby="doctrine-heading">
        <p class="section-label">Doctrine / manifestos</p>
        <h2 id="doctrine-heading">The operating language belongs here.</h2>
        <div class="callout">
          <h3>Doctrine Lane</h3>
          <p>Field doctrine, systems manifestos, and archive principles should publish through Le Signal, then remain searchable in L'Archive.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="field-reports" class="signal-section" aria-labelledby="field-report-heading">
        <p class="section-label">{{ archive.fieldLogs | count }} reports</p>
        <h2 id="field-report-heading">Field reports are authored signal, not live feed.</h2>
        {% if archive.fieldLogs.length %}
        <ol class="field-note-list">
          {% for log in archive.fieldLogs | reverse %}
          <li class="field-note-card">
            <header>
              <time datetime="{{ log.date }}">{{ log.date | replace('-', '.') | replace('-', '.') }}</time>
              <span>{{ log.category }}</span>
            </header>
            <h3>{{ log.title }}</h3>
            <p>{{ log.object }}. {{ log.status }}.</p>
          </li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ol>
        {% else %}
        <div class="callout field-note-empty">
          <h3>No Reports Yet</h3>
          <p>The lane is active. Add structured field-log records when a report is ready for the authored signal.</p>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
